<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Services</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #d789c4;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #e39cc2; 
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed; 
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0; 
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end; 
            gap: 10px;
            z-index: 1000; 
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff; 
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 10px; 
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 80px auto 0; 
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .service-card h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: #555;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
        
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Product Sourcing</h2>
            <p>We help you find the best products from trusted suppliers. 
            Our team ensures every item meets quality standards, bringing
            you closer to reliable and high-grade merchandise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Custom Orders</h2>
            <p>Need something specific? We offer custom ordering options 
            to meet your unique requirements. Just let us know what you're 
            looking for, and we'll make it happen!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Fast & Reliable Delivery</h2>
            <p>We understand the importance of getting your products on time. 
            That's why we offer fast, reliable delivery to your door, so you 
            can enjoy your purchases without any hassle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Customer Support</h2>
            <p>Our team is here to assist you with any queries or concerns. 
            From product selection to post-purchase support, we're with you 
            every step of the way.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
